The paper focuses on image captioning, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of deep learning models such as LSTM and CNN also suggests that it could belong to sub-categories related to machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the evaluation of the proposed models on benchmark datasets involves information retrieval tasks (cs.IR).
